  %p There are various ways to keep up with what's happening in our community.
  %ul
    %li
      Twitter:
      %a{href: 'http://twitter.com/rubyaustralia'} @rubyaustralia
    %li
      Mailing list:
      %a{href: 'https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/rails-oceania'} Ruby/Rails Oceania
    %li
      IRC:
      %a{href: 'irc://irc.freenode.net/roro'} #roro
      or online via
      %a{href: 'http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=roro'} freenode webchat
      or
      %a{href: 'http://kiwiirc.com/client/irc.freenode.net/roro'} Kiwi IRC
    %li
      Catch up on
      %a{href: 'https://vimeo.com/rubyau/channels'} talks from RubyConfAU and #rorosyd
